text: I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here! returned for its nineteenth series on 17 November 2019 on ITV. This series featured McPartlin's return as the show’s co-host, who was replaced by This Morning co-presenter Holly Willoughby in 2018, after deciding to take a year’s hiatus from television. He appeared again alongside Declan Donnelly. The series opening episode was watched by 13.17 million people. Category:I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here! Category:2019 television seasons
title: I'm a Celebrity…Get Me Out of Here! (British TV series 19)
